      "settings": {
        "use_own_file": true,
        "active": false,
        "must_read": true,
        "heading": "Content Requirements",
        "text": "<h2>Content Requirements</h2><p>Messaging must include:</p><ul><li>This device combines red light therapy and low-level laser therapy (LLLT) to help stimulate hair follicles and promote regrowth.</li><li>The Q-Renew LLLT Helmet is a safe at-home solution for thinning hair — just 12 minutes per day, a few times per week.</li><li>Lightweight, wireless, and rechargeable with an adjustable fit, making it easy to use anytime, anywhere.</li><li>Features a smart LCD screen that allows users to target specific treatment zones for a customized experience.</li><li>Built-in safety sensors, auto-pause functionality, and a 3-year warranty ensure peace of mind with every treatment.</li></ul>",
        "slides_per_view": ""
      }
    },
