        "heading": "Creative Direction",
        "text": "<h2>Creative Direction</h2><p>Recording Guidelines</p><ul><li>Use bright, natural lighting. No filters.</li><li>Ensure the Qure Q-Renew LLLT Helmet is the main focus of the content.</li><li>Keep backgrounds clean and uncluttered.</li><li>In cover photos for video content always show yourself using the Q-Renew LLLT Helmet (unless agreed otherwise).</li><li>Before and after imaging to showcase the results, if possible.</li></ul>",
