      "blocks": {
        "text_slider_7WWG98": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>My Transformation Journey (Before & After)</strong></p><p>Share a personal or follower story about hair thinning and its impact on confidence, focusing on the challenges faced and the journey to finding a solution. Show yourself using the Q-Renew Helmet over weeks, talking about how easy it is to fit into daily life. Share a before and after.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>Show the helmet routine over weeks, talking about how easy it is to fit into daily life. Share a before and after.[/note]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_QrLQz4": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Daily Routine Integration</strong></p><p>Show how simple the 12-minute treatment is with a GRWM or nigh routine, where the Q-Renew Helmet is used in a relaxed setting, such as while reading, scrolling TikTok, etc. too emphasize its ease of use and convenience.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong></p><ul><li>“This helmet is the easiest part of my night routine… and the one part that’s actually working.”</li><li>“This is everything I do while my hair grows back…”</li></ul><p>[/note]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_CkyYD9": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Tech & Innovation Highlight</strong></p><p>Present the Q-Renew Helmet as a cutting-edge beauty/wellness device with an unboxing or tech-demo style video. Draw attention to the 370 lights, LCD screen, adjustable fit, and wireless charging dock.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong></p><ul><li>“Unboxing the hair growth device that looks straight out of the future…”</li><li>“If Apple made a hair growth device, it would look like this.”</li></ul><p>[/note]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_7KXdyw": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Confidence & Self-Care Routine</strong></p><p>Position hair growth as part of self-care and confidence building, talking about how investing in your hair is investing in your confidence. Pair the helmet with your other wellness/beauty rituals.</p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>“For me, growing my hair back hasn’t just been about looks. It’s been about feeling like myself again, and that’s why I count it as part of my self-care routine.”[/note]</p>"
          }
        },
        "text_slider_tBPeBn": {
          "type": "text_slider",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Expert/Authority-Driven Education</strong></p><p>Educate the audience on red light therapy and Low-Level Laser Therapy (LLLT) in simple, easy-to-understand terms. Break down how the light stimulates hair follicles, increases blood flow, and supports natural regrowth without using complex medical jargon. </p><p>[note_grey]<strong>Hook:</strong>“Did you know that red light therapy can stimulate follicles and support regrowth? Here’s how the Q-Renew Helmet makes it easy at home.”[/note]</p>"
          }
        }
